{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"alias":"self-ledge-seam","description":"# Fix stale doc/comment references surfaced by the 2026-07-02 audit\n\n## What\nPure documentation/comment corrections (zero behavior change) found by the audit and\nverified against source. Already implemented in commits on `fix/completion-child-scope`.\n\nFiles: `docs/exit-codes.md` (stale `ticket_reads.py`), `src/rebar/_reads.py` (docstring cited\n3 deleted files), `docs/workflow-engine.md` (\"two gates\" -> three), `docs/architecture.md`\n(duplicate attest.py row + stale reconcile_once remedy), `docs/output-schemas.md` (7 missing\nrows + coverage-guard overclaim), `src/rebar/llm/prompts_frontmatter.py` (wrong key list),\n`reconcile.py` + `gate_ops.py` (stale line-number citations).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] All cited stale references corrected and verified against source.\n- [ ] `make lint` (ruff check + format) passes.\n- [ ] Commit carries a `rebar-ticket:` trailer; lands through Gerrit.","id":"cc4f-0224-19a2-4115","parent_id":"9322-f84a-e047-4471","priority":1,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Fix stale doc/comment references surfaced by the audit"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783053679143514001,"uuid":"e7f7e6cf-d376-4398-91b2-91b77d005d08"}